#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg; is simple log viewer for &gnupg;. It works as a &GUI; wrapper "
"around the command line tool &watchgnupg;, which listens on a socket for log "
"lines from the &gnupg; backend applications. See <userinput>info watchgnupg</"
"userinput> for more information about &watchgnupg;."
msgstr ""
"&kwatchgnupg;是 &gnupg; 的简单日志查看器。它作为一个&GUI;命令行工具 "
"&watchgnupg; 的包装器，它在套接字上监听来自 &gnupg; 的日志行。后端应用程序。"
"有关 &watchgnupg; 的更多信息，请参阅 <userinput>watchgnupg 信息</userinput>。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg; can be started from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>GnuPG Log Viewer</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of "
"both &kleopatra; and &kmail;, as well as from the command line. The "
"&kwatchgnupg; executable is named <userinput>kwatchgnupg</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kwatchgnupg; 可以通过 &kleopatra; 和 &kmail; 的 <menuchoice><guimenu>工具</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>GnuPG 日志查看器</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 菜单启动，也"
"可以从命令行启动。&kwatchgnupg; 的可执行文件名为 <userinput>kwatchgnupg</"
"userinput>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Functions"
msgstr "主要功能"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing the Log"
msgstr "查看日志"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg;'s main function is of course to present the &gnupg; debugging "
"and logging information to the user. The main window is divided into a large "
"text viewing area, where &gnupg; messages will appear as they are generated, "
"a toolbar giving quick access to the most often needed functions, as well as "
"the obligatory menu bar."
msgstr ""
"&kwatchgnupg; 的主要功能当然是向用户显示 &gnupg; 的调试和日志信息。主窗口分为"
"几个部分：一个较大的文本查看区域，用于按生成顺序显示 &gnupg; 消息；一个工具"
"栏，用于快速访问最常用的功能；以及必不可少的菜单栏。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each line in the text view is normally prefixed with a <acronym>FD</acronym> "
"identifier and a time stamp in ISO format. The <acronym>FD</acronym> "
"identifier can be used to distinguish between output from different &gnupg; "
"instances running in parallel. Following the timestamp is the name of the "
"component that is the source of the log line, together with some internal "
"information in sqare brackets, followed by the original debugging or log "
"output as printed by the component."
msgstr ""
"文本视图中的每一行通常以前缀形式显示一个 <acronym>FD</acronym> 标识符以及一"
"个 ISO 格式的时间戳。<acronym>FD</acronym> 标识符可用于区分并行运行的不同 "
"&gnupg; 实例所产生的输出。时间戳之后是生成该日志行的组件名称，随后是方括号中"
"的一些内部信息，最后是该组件输出的原始调试或日志信息。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the number of log lines that are kept in the history is limited "
"to 10000 lines. You can configure the history size in the configuration "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，历史记录中保留的日志行数限制为 10000 行。你可以在配置对话框中调整"
"历史记录的大小。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving the Contents of the Log Window to a File"
msgstr "正在将日志窗口的内容保存到文件"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes it might be convenient to save the current log window contents to "
"a file, &eg; to mail it to the developers as part of a bug report. There are "
"two ways to achieve this in &kwatchgnupg;:"
msgstr ""
"有时，将当前日志窗口的内容保存到文件中可能会比较方便，&eg; 作为错误报告的一部"
"分通过电子邮件发送给开发者。在 &kwatchgnupg; 中可以通过以下两种方式实现这一"
"点："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you can choose <menuchoice><guilabel>File</guilabel><guimenuitem>Save "
"As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (or the corresponding toolbar icon) to save "
"the complete log window contents to a file. You will be prompted to specify "
"a save file location."
msgstr ""
"第一种方式是选择 <menuchoice><guilabel>文件</guilabel><guimenuitem>另存为..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>（或点击相应的工具栏图标），将完整的日志窗口内容保"
"存到文件中。系统会提示你指定保存文件的位置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Second, you can select the interesting lines with normal left-mouse "
"selection and paste them into a word processor or mail user agent, just like "
"any other text. You should make sure, though, that lines are not broken, "
"since this reduces the readability of the log."
msgstr ""
"第二种方式是使用鼠标左键的常规选择方式选中感兴趣的行，然后像处理正常文本一"
"样，将其粘贴到文字处理程序或邮件客户端中。不过请务必确保不要将行拆分，因为这"
"会降低日志的可读性。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clearing the Log Window"
msgstr "正在清除日志窗口"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For convenience, you can instruct &kwatchgnupg; to clear the log window "
"using <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear History</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (or the corresponding toolbar icon)."
msgstr ""
"为了方便起见，你可以通过 <menuchoice><guimenu>文件</guimenu><guimenuitem>清空"
"历史记录</guimenuitem></menuchoice>（或相应的工具栏图标）指示 &kwatchgnupg; "
"清空日志窗口。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this prior to starting the crypto operation that you want to monitor to "
"get only the output from that operation. You can then save the log using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> as described above."
msgstr ""
"在开始你希望监视的加密操作之前使用此功能，可以确保只获得该操作产生的输出。随"
"后你可以按照上述说明，通过 <menuchoice><guimenu>文件</guimenu><guimenuitem>另"
"存为...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 保存日志。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clearing the log discards any previous log window contents. If you are "
"unsure about whether you'll need the current contents afterwards, you should "
"save them to a file (see above) before clearing."
msgstr ""
"清空日志将丢弃日志窗口中此前的所有内容。如果你不确定之后是否还需要当前内容，"
"建议在清空之前先将其保存到文件中（见上文）。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kwatchgnupg;"
msgstr "配置 &kwatchgnupg;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure &kwatchgnupg;, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kwatchgnupg;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or "
"the corresponding toolbar icon."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "设置对话框"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Log Window Settings"
msgstr "日志窗口设置"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can configure the size of the history buffer, &ie; the number of "
"log lines that is kept. If more lines have been emitted by the &gnupg; "
"backend since the last clearance of the history, then the oldest lines are "
"discarded until there is enough room for the new lines again."
msgstr ""
"在此可以配置历史缓冲区的大小，&ie; 保留的日志行数。如果自上次清空历史记录以"
"来，&gnupg; 后端生成的日志行数超过该限制，则会丢弃最旧的行，直到为新日志行腾"
"出足够的空间为止。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can disable the history size limit by clicking <guibutton>Set Unlimited</"
"guibutton>. Note, however, that &kwatchgnupg;'s memory consumption will grow "
"with the number of lines it currently displays. If you use an unlimited "
"history size, then make sure to run &kwatchgnupg; only for short operations, "
"or regularly clear the history manually."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过单击 <guibutton>设为无限</guibutton> 来禁用历史记录大小限制。不过请"
"注意，&kwatchgnupg; 的内存占用会随着当前显示的行数增加而增长。如果使用无限的"
"历史记录大小，请确保仅在短时间操作时运行 &GnuPG 监视器; 或定期手动清空历史记"
"录。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gnupg; Logging Settings"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the settings dialog of &kleopatra; for configuring logging of the "
"components of the &gnupg; System. For each component for which you want to "
"see logging choose a debugging level and enter <filename>socket://</"
"filename> as file the logs should be written to."
msgstr ""

